WEBVTT

00:05.871 --> 00:09.168
Shirley, I am not going through this again.

00:09.210 --> 00:10.921
Would someone catch me up here?

00:10.921 --> 00:12.340
Denny got engaged.

00:12.382 --> 00:14.468
–Mazel tov?
–No mazel tov.

00:14.510 --> 00:16.303
–Who is it this time?
–Beverly Bridge.

00:16.303 --> 00:17.932
The woman Denny “craned” in the

00:17.932 --> 00:19.685
coatroom at that charity dinner last week.

00:19.685 --> 00:22.774
If this Bev turns out to be
another Angie, oh, God!

00:22.857 --> 00:24.443
–Angie?
–Number four.

00:24.527 --> 00:26.204
Wife number five was no picnic either.

00:26.204 --> 00:26.942
Clovis.

00:26.977 --> 00:28.211
She most got him to retire,

00:28.211 --> 00:30.546
pull his equity out of the firm
and move to Boca.

00:30.546 --> 00:33.159
–Clovis nearly sunk us.
–Half the staff quit.

00:33.159 --> 00:36.281
And she was drunk the day
president Ford stopped by.

00:36.337 --> 00:40.225
All right, I'll pull out Denny's last prenup,
see if I can water-seal it.

00:40.225 --> 00:42.779
Shirley, you talk to the woman.
Get her story.

00:42.779 --> 00:45.335
Brad, check the partnership agreement.

00:45.370 --> 00:46.823
We have to be sure there are no

00:46.823 --> 00:48.206
loopholes in the mandatory buyout

00:48.206 --> 00:50.505
in case of a partner's death or incapacity.

00:50.505 --> 00:52.164
–One thing.
–What?

00:52.199 --> 00:56.454
Is there any remote possibility
we could be overreacting here?

00:59.209 --> 01:05.510
