01:05.594 --> 01:09.560
♫ I've never felt this way before ♫

01:09.643 --> 01:14.693
♫ Yes, I swear it's the truth Oh, it's true ♫

01:14.776 --> 01:16.362
♫ and I owe it all to you ♫

01:16.362 --> 01:20.883
♫ because I had the time of my life ♫

01:20.918 --> 01:25.404
I'll get the partnership agreement.

